messages.messageBody:
In a message dated 10/19/2005 2:01:37 PM Eastern Daylight Time,
KathrynJB@... writes:

I'm noticing that lots of you are in the northeast!!!! Well, just for early
warning, I've just booked with a space to hold a Northeast Unschooling
Gathering on Memorial Day Weekend, May 26-29ish, 2006 in Peabody, Massachusetts.
I'll have more details soon, and hopefully a website, but I wanted to give
people lots of notice.

I'm open to any ideas (with no guarantees).
Kathryn Baptista



~~~~~~~~~~
Oh awesome! Something I could definitely plan for... :o)

Jenny
Mom to Danny, Kelsey and Evelyn
Happily homeschooling in Greenfield, MA
~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~
Learning is a treasure that will follow its owner everywhere. ~Chinese
